| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7496 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4e0cc03b-4bf3-5d56-b798-4bd2eb838b74"
